Welcome,
Here you can find Pictures and documents for use for Publications.
For any further information please email press@bouroullec.com

Rights and Usages
Consider that all the pictures you might get from us are free for any personal use, public presentation or press publication, but for any commercial use please contact us.
You may not modify or store these images in a retrieval system.
Please credit the photographer.
Please do not forget to send us a copy of your article when released.

Thank you in advance !

Nota Bene
The picture files are provided as Zip archive, on mac use the "finder" or "stuffit expander" to expand the archive. On Windows use "unzip".
Some files are also privided as PDF, you need to have "acrobat reader" from adobe (on mac os 10.3 + you can also use "aperçu")
